### Sales API - Create Order Endpoint
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### Create Order - Basic Request
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "idempotencyKey": "unique-key-123456",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "prod-001",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 29.99,
      "name": "Sample Product"
    }
  ],
  "amount": 59.98
}

### Create Order - With Multiple Items
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-456",
  "idempotencyKey": "unique-key-12345",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "prod-001",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 29.99,
      "name": "Product 1"
    },
    {
      "productId": "prod-002",
      "quantity": 3,
      "price": 15.50,
      "name": "Product 2"
    }
  ],
  "amount": 76.49,
  "idempotencyKey": "unique-key-12345"
}

